content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?> <rdf:RDF      xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#"      xmlns:rdfs="http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#"      xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"      xmlns:dcq="http://dublincore.org/2000/03/13/dcq#"      xmlns:lom="http://www.imsproject.org/rdf/imsmd_rootv1p2#"      xmlns:lom_gen="http://www.imsproject.org/rdf/imsmd_generalv1p2#">    <rdf:Property rdf:ID="catalogentry">     <rdfs:label>Catalog Entry</rdfs:label>     <rdfs:comment>An entry in a catalog.</rdfs:comment>   </rdf:Property>      <rdfs:Class rdf:ID="Structure">     <rdfs:label>Structure types</rdfs:label>     <rdfs:comment>Instances of this class represent organizational structures.</rdfs:comment>   </rdfs:Class>      <lom_gen:Structure ID="Collection"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Mixed"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Linear"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Hierarchical"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Networked"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Branched"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Parceled"/>   <lom_gen:Structure ID="Atomic"/>    <rdf:Property rdf:ID="structure">     <rdf:range rdf:resource="#Structure"/>     <rdfs:label>Structure</rdfs:label>     <rdfs:comment>Underlying organizational structure of the learning object.</rdfs:comment>   </rdf:Property>      <rdfs:Class rdf:ID="AggregationLevel">     <rdfs:label>Aggregation levels</rdfs:label>     <rdfs:comment>Instances of this class represent aggregation levels.</rdfs:comment>   </rdfs:Class>      <lom_gen:AggregationLevel ID="Level1"/>   <lom_gen:AggregationLevel ID="Level2"/>   <lom_gen:AggregationLevel ID="Level3"/>   <lom_gen:AggregationLevel ID="Level4"/>     <rdf:Property rdf:ID="aggregationlevel">     <rdf:range rdf:resource="#AggregationLevel"/>     <rdfs:label>Aggregation Level</rdfs:label>     <rdfs:comment>The functional granularity of the learning object.</rdfs:comment>   </rdf:Property>  </rdf:RDF>
